<template>
  <v-list-item :class="indent ? 'ml-8' : ''">
    <v-list-item-content>
      <v-list-item-title>
        {{ name }}: <span class="font-weight-regular grey--text text--darken-2" v-html="value || '-'" />
      </v-list-item-title>
    </v-list-item-content>
  </v-list-item>
</template>

  export default {
    props: {
      name: { type: String, default: '' },
      value: { type: [String, Number], default: '' },
      indent: { type: Boolean, default: true },
    },
  }
</script>
